<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
    <!--Landing page of the website-->
	<title>Homepage</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/Homepage.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/General.css">

    <!--BOOTSTRAP Links-->
    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
</head>
<body>
    <%- include ("./partials/Navbar") %>
    <%- include ("./partials/FlashMessage") %>

    <!--Header of the page-->
    <div class="container title">
        <h1>Science Twins</h1>
        <h5>Digital twins for scientific experiments</h5>
    </div>
    <!--Second section of the page, containing the different functionalities of the app-->
    <div class="introduction">
        <h2><span class="line">What to Do?</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <!--The following row and columns contain the different functionalities of the app-->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-3 left-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a7 7 0 1 0 14 0A7 7 0 0 0 1 8zm15 0A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zM4.5 7.5a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h5.793l-2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708l3-3a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 1 0-.708.708L10.293 7.5H4.5z"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="col-9">
                <h3><a href="./experiment/pastexperiments">Past Experiments</a></h3>
                <p>Here you can find and replay the different experiments uploaded by the users on the platform.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-9">
                <h3><a href="./experiment/upload-experiment">Upload Experiment</a></h3>
                <p>Here you can upload an experiment to the webapplication provided that you have a video of it and some recorded data from the sensors so that other users will be able to view it</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 right-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-left-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a7 7 0 1 0 14 0A7 7 0 0 0 1 8zm15 0A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zm-4.5-.5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H5.707l2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708l3-3a.5.5 0 1 1 .708.708L5.707 7.5H11.5z"/>
                  </svg>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-3 left-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a7 7 0 1 0 14 0A7 7 0 0 0 1 8zm15 0A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zM4.5 7.5a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h5.793l-2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708l3-3a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 1 0-.708.708L10.293 7.5H4.5z"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="col-9">
                <h3><a href="./experiment/create-live" onclick="askPermission(); return false;">Create Live</a></h3>
                <p>Here you can create a live stream for an experiment. You will need to choose a streaming camera and the data to be displayed. On top of that you will be able to connect your sensors to the application to get live data!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-9">
                <!--By clicking this link the a modal form opens to input name and password for the stream-->
                <h3><a href="#" onclick="joinRoom()">Join Live</a></h3>
                <p>Click this button to join an already existing livestream providing the name and password of the room you want to enter</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 right-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-left-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a7 7 0 1 0 14 0A7 7 0 0 0 1 8zm15 0A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zm-4.5-.5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H5.707l2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708l3-3a.5.5 0 1 1 .708.708L5.707 7.5H11.5z"/>
                  </svg>
            </div>
            <!--Modal which 'opens' once the user wants to join a livestream, displaying a form with the name and password of the room to join-->
            <div class="modal" id="joinLiveModal">
                <div class="modal-form">
                    <form action="./experiment/join-live" method="POST">
                        <label for="roomName">Name for live:</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="roomName" name="roomName"
                          placeholder="Room name" required>
                        <label for="roomPassword">Password for live:</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="roomPassword" name="roomPassword"
                          required>
                        <button  type="submit">Join Live</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
<script src="js/Homepage.js"></script>
</html>